FROM [Orders] AS [o]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o1].[OrderItemId], [o1].[OrderId], [o1].[ProductId], [o1].[Quantity], [p0].[ProductId] AS [ProductId0], [p0].[BrandId], [p0].[CategoryId], [p0].[Price], [p0].[ProductImage], [p0].[ProductName], [p0].[ProductStatusId], [p0].[Quantity] AS [Quantity0], [p0].[StoreId], [p0].[SubCategoryId]
    FROM [OrderItems] AS [o1]
    LEFT JOIN [Products] AS [p0] ON [o1].[ProductId] = [p0].[ProductId]
) AS [t] ON [o].[OrderId] = [t].[OrderId]
WHERE EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM [OrderItems] AS [o0]
    LEFT JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [o0].[ProductId] = [p].[ProductId]
    WHERE ([o].[OrderId] = [o0].[OrderId]) AND (([p].[ProductId] IS NOT NULL) AND ([p].[StoreId] = @__storeId_0)))

FROM [Orders] AS [o]

    SELECT [o1].[OrderItemId], [o1].[OrderId], [o1].[ProductId], [o1].[Quantity], [p0].[ProductId] AS [ProductId0], [p0].[BrandId], [p0].[CategoryId], [p0].[Price], [p0].[ProductImage], [p0].[ProductName], [p0].[ProductStatusId], [p0].[Quantity] AS [Quantity0], [p0].[StoreId], [p0].[SubCategoryId]
    FROM [OrderItems] AS [o1]
    LEFT JOIN [Products] AS [p0] ON [o1].[ProductId] = [p0].[ProductId]
) AS [t] ON [o].[OrderId] = [t].[OrderId]
WHERE EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM [OrderItems] AS [o0]
    LEFT JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [o0].[ProductId] = [p].[ProductId]
    WHERE ([o].[OrderId] = [o0].[OrderId]) AND (([p].[ProductId] IS NOT NULL) AND ([p].[StoreId] = @__storeId_0)))
ORDER BY [o].[OrderId], [t].[OrderItemId]

FROM [Orders] AS [o]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o1].[OrderItemId], [o1].[OrderId], [o1].[ProductId], [o1].[Quantity], [p0].[ProductId] AS [ProductId0], [p0].[BrandId], [p0].[CategoryId], [p0].[Price], [p0].[ProductImage], [p0].[ProductName], [p0].[ProductStatusId], [p0].[Quantity] AS [Quantity0], [p0].[StoreId], [p0].[SubCategoryId]
    FROM [OrderItems] AS [o1]
    LEFT JOIN [Products] AS [p0] ON [o1].[ProductId] = [p0].[ProductId]
) AS [t] ON [o].[OrderId] = [t].[OrderId]

    SELECT 1
    FROM [OrderItems] AS [o0]
    LEFT JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [o0].[ProductId] = [p].[ProductId]

FROM [Orders] AS [o]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o1].[OrderItemId], [o1].[OrderId], [o1].[ProductId], [o1].[Quantity], [p0].[ProductId] AS [ProductId0], [p0].[BrandId], [p0].[CategoryId], [p0].[Price], [p0].[ProductImage], [p0].[ProductName], [p0].[ProductStatusId], [p0].[Quantity] AS [Quantity0], [p0].[StoreId], [p0].[SubCategoryId]
    FROM [OrderItems] AS [o1]
    LEFT JOIN [Products] AS [p0] ON [o1].[ProductId] = [p0].[ProductId]
) AS [t] ON [o].[OrderId] = [t].[OrderId]
WHERE EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM [OrderItems] AS [o0]
    LEFT JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [o0].[ProductId] = [p].[ProductId]
    WHERE ([o].[OrderId] = [o0].[OrderId]) AND (([p].[ProductId] IS NOT NULL) AND ([p].[StoreId] = @__storeId_0)))

FROM [Orders] AS [o]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o1].[OrderItemId], [o1].[OrderId], [o1].[ProductId], [o1].[Quantity], [p0].[ProductId] AS [ProductId0], [p0].[BrandId], [p0].[CategoryId], [p0].[Price], [p0].[ProductImage], [p0].[ProductName], [p0].[ProductStatusId], [p0].[Quantity] AS [Quantity0], [p0].[StoreId], [p0].[SubCategoryId]
    FROM [OrderItems] AS [o1]
    LEFT JOIN [Products] AS [p0] ON [o1].[ProductId] = [p0].[ProductId]
) AS [t] ON [o].[OrderId] = [t].[OrderId]
WHERE EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM [OrderItems] AS [o0]
    LEFT JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [o0].[ProductId] = [p].[ProductId]
    WHERE ([o].[OrderId] = [o0].[OrderId]) AND (([p].[ProductId] IS NOT NULL) AND ([p].[StoreId] = @__storeId_0)))
